task.summary: Default task
Config initial commit on the new branch.
Test commit.
Refactoring the database configuration to use java classes, dao objects replaced with spring data repositories and changes in logic regarding introduction of those.
Further refactoring of configuration to use full java, security configuration fails to work.
Security config fixed.
Runtime exception handling on authentication process added, removed service interfaces in favor of classes.
Angular.js front support initial commit.
Added schema migration with flyway. Configuration for angular working.
Schema migration fixed. Configuration for angular working but there are problems with library loading.
Station and some user data retrieving using angular added. Logic for renting/returning bike not finished yet.
Renting/returning bike logic introduced to the front and back controllers.
Basic security using angular started. There are still some issues.

Stateless spring security finished, still may need some improvements, JwtHelper class is able to obtain the values for key and token expiration time from properties file. Started the reimplementation of the application services using new controllers.
Further redeployment of the cbrs system. Reset password, registration and resending of activation link, payment service fixed.
Added timer implementation to the service, still needs fixes. Basic reimplementation of admin panel and user roles' adjustments.
Fixed the problem with missing role on authentication, introduced the lambda expression in the authentication filter.
Introduced basic admin services, started refactoring the userpanel UI.
Reimplementation of admin services continue, changes in user and admin panel to use the ui router angular framework.
Admin services done with angular, might need other adjustments.
Exception handling adjusted to use rest responses, some fixes still required. Further adjustments in the admin panel, old implementation cleanup.
Severe problem with redirection after data requests. Introduced authentication failure handler to respond with json object. Some other application cleanup.
Last commit before review. Problems with redirection fixed.
